    "Additionally, artificial intelligence algorithms will help patients by swiftly, easily, and accurately resolving this problem.",
    "The vast training of radiologists in this field is a key aspect.",
    "AI can aid in making a precise diagnosis in radiology [9].",
    "Convolutional neural networks, among other deep learningbased AI systems, were employed in conjunction with chest x-rays to get accurate results utilising COVID-19.",
    "This is so because CNNs can learn the features on their own without the user having to extract them."
